==English==

===Verb===
{{en-verb|depav|ing}}

# To undo the act of [[pave|paving]]; to remove [[pavement]] so as to restore the land to a more natural state.
#:*Even though it caused much controversy, Mayor Daley was eventually lauded as a hero for his decision to '''depave''' Lake Shore Drive.

